Mimoiš'o sam te.

113
00:09:13,625 --> 00:09:15,916
Kal, prestani.
Ovo nije smešno.

114
00:09:18,208 --> 00:09:19,041
Beki?

115
00:09:19,833 --> 00:09:20,666
Da?

116
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,875
