Hajde da uradimo ono.

127
00:09:51,375 --> 00:09:52,375
U redu?

128
00:09:52,458 --> 00:09:53,743
Spreman?
- U redu.

129
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,375
Jedan, dva, tri!

130
00:10:00,166 --> 00:10:01,351
Blizu si.

131
00:10:01,541 --> 00:10:02,656
Još jednom.

132
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,791
U redu.
- Jedan, dva, tri.

133
00:10:15,708 --> 00:10:17,788
Ovo je ludo!
Ovo je jebeno ludilo.

134
00:10:17,923 --> 00:10:18,798
Beki!

135
00:10:19,333 --> 00:10:20,291
Beki!

136
00:10:21,958 --> 00:10:24,041
Beki!
 <i>- Ovde sam!</i>

137
00:10:27,294 --> 00:10:28,127
Bek!

138
