Ovde!

141
00:10:34,458 --> 00:10:35,625
Beki!

142
00:11:16,916 --> 00:11:19,250
Kal? Jesi li uredu?
Šta je bilo?

143
00:11:21,708 --> 00:11:22,828
Ništa!

144
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:26,225
Samo sam se okliznuo.

145
00:11:30,291 --> 00:11:32,233
Malo mi je čudno.

146
00:11:32,541 --> 00:11:33,625
Šta da radimo?

147
00:11:34,624 --> 00:11:36,523
Idemo odavde.

148
00:11:36,708 --> 00:11:38,772
Samo moramo
da ostanemo pribrani.

149
00:11:39,291 --> 00:11:41,767
