Beki!

154
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:05,666
Kal?

155
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,666
Beki.

156
00:12:08,375 --> 00:12:09,345
Kal.

157
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,875
