Ne mrdaj.

158
00:12:13,916 --> 00:12:15,166
Čuvaj glas.

159
00:12:16,083 --> 00:12:17,333
Doći ću do tebe.

160
00:12:46,041 --> 00:12:47,387
Beki!

161
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,458
Bek!

162
00:12:50,541 --> 00:12:51,583
Kal?

