190
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:54,166
Tobin?

191
00:14:54,826 --> 00:14:57,592
Polje ne pomera
mrtve stvari okolo.

192
00:15:05,875 --> 00:15:07,135
Tobine...

193
00:15:09,583 --> 00:15:11,752
da li ste nas namamili unutra?

194
