199
00:15:25,502 --> 00:15:26,377
Čoveka.

200
00:15:27,859 --> 00:15:29,150
Zvao je pomoć.

201
00:15:30,416 --> 00:15:31,839
Tako smo ušli.

202
00:15:32,708 --> 00:15:34,128
Tako to radi.

203
00:15:34,666 --> 00:15:36,583
Koliko dugo si ovde?

204
00:15:36,666 --> 00:15:38,135
Nisam siguran.

205
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,375
Beki...

206
00:15:43,541 --> 00:15:44,926
tvoja sestra...

207
00:15:47,833 --> 00:15:49,809
uskoro će umreti.

208
00:16:01,791 --> 00:16:03,625
Kako znaš da mi je sestra?

209
00:16:03,958 --> 00:16:04,833
Kamen.

210
00:16:05,541 --> 00:16:07,963
Kamen te uči da
čuješ visoku travu.

211
00:16:08,166 --> 00:16:09,791
Visoka trava zna sve.

212
00:16:13,166 --> 00:16:14,000
Onda...

213
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,609
moraš da znaš gde je.

214
00:16:17,416 --> 00:16:18,473
Jel' da?

215
00:16:19,583 --> 00:16:21,692
Mogu ti otkriti.

216
00:16:22,916 --> 00:16:23,750
Ne...

217
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,875
Mogu i bolje od toga.

218
00:16:27,416 --> 00:16:28,739
Mogu ti pokazati.

219
00:16:29,833 --> 00:16:30,916
Želiš li da je vidiš?

220
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:33,028
Da je nađeš?

221
00:16:33,090 --> 00:16:34,965
Hajde, prati me.

222
00:16:51,507 --> 00:16:52,673
Koliko si trudna?

223
00:16:54,791 --> 00:16:56,208
Šest meseci.

224
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:00,517
Sećam se kad je
Natali bila trudna.

225
00:17:02,125 --> 00:17:03,708
To su bili dani salate.

226
00:17:03,791 --> 00:17:04,895
Uživaj.

227
00:17:05,469 --> 00:17:07,637
Uživaj u svojoj
bebi, jer brzo će.

228
00:17:12,892 --> 00:17:14,425
Tata nije na slici?

229
00:17:17,208 --> 00:17:18,816
Nije bio spreman za to.

230
00:17:19,124 --> 00:17:20,971
Baš loše od njega.

231
00:17:23,415 --> 00:17:24,290
Znaš...

232
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:26,208
porodica je sve.

233
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:30,125
Ako postoji jedna stvar
koju sigurno znam,

234
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:32,666
to je ta jednostavna istina.

235
00:17:33,958 --> 00:17:35,471
Bolje da krenemo.

236
00:17:36,083 --> 00:17:38,315
Što pre dođemo do
njih, to bolje.

237
00:17:56,250 --> 00:17:57,125
Ros?

238
00:18:15,791 --> 00:18:16,625
Kal!

239
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,982
Jesi li tamo?

240
00:18:20,416 --> 00:18:21,250
Kal?

